416
00:16:27,040 --> 00:16:27,680
Zengzi once said,

417
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:28,960
the way of great learning consists in

418
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:30,080
manifesting one's bright virtue,

419
00:16:30,043 --> 00:16:32,358
[Ge Jianhao, Mother of Cai Hesen]

420
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:31,120
in loving the people,

421
00:16:31,280 --> 00:16:32,560
in aiming at absolute perfection.

422
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:33,600
If you renew yourself for one day,

423
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:34,560
you can renew yourself daily

424
00:16:34,720 --> 00:16:35,520
and continue to do so.

425
00:16:34,737 --> 00:16:36,433
[He Shuheng, styled Yuheng]

426
00:16:36,160 --> 00:16:36,640
I think

427
00:16:36,918 --> 00:16:38,112
[Cai Hesen, styled Runhuan]

428
00:16:37,040 --> 00:16:38,320
to be part of the new generation

429
00:16:38,400 --> 00:16:40,560
is everyone's purpose.

430
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:41,760
Hence,

431
00:16:42,080 --> 00:16:44,160
our new organization will be called "Xinmin Society"
(Xinmin: new generation)

432
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:44,960
Xinmin Society.

