440
00:17:04,560 --> 00:17:05,200
Dear members,

441
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:07,280
our organization

442
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:09,520
is born from the New Culture Movement.

443
00:17:09,840 --> 00:17:10,640
Its specialty

444
00:17:10,800 --> 00:17:11,840
is its spirit.

445
00:17:12,080 --> 00:17:12,720
There is only one element,

446
00:17:13,120 --> 00:17:14,080
which is "New".

447
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:15,040
Hence,

448
00:17:15,280 --> 00:17:16,240
we will need to use new ways of thinking,

449
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:17,440
new cultures,

450
00:17:17,600 --> 00:17:18,320
new theories

451
00:17:18,400 --> 00:17:20,080
to equip our members' thoughts,

452
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:22,080
change our morals for the better,

453
00:17:22,560 --> 00:17:24,080
and improve our knowledge

454
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:26,640
This is our organization's intention

455
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:27,760
and responsibility.

456
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:28,400
Hence,

457
00:17:28,640 --> 00:17:30,400
I believe our organization's purpose

458
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:31,920
is to spark innovations in education,

459
00:17:32,320 --> 00:17:33,200
strengthen character,

460
00:17:33,440 --> 00:17:35,440
improve people's way of thinking and customs.

461
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:36,640
Therefore,

462
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:37,360
The organization stipulates that

463
00:17:37,840 --> 00:17:39,680
every member must accomplish the following:

464
00:17:39,760 --> 00:17:40,800
first, to not be hypocritical;

465
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:42,320
second, to not be lazy;

466
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:43,840
third, to not be wasteful;

467
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:44,960
